description:
Chic studio near Central Park

Cosy studio in the heart of the Upper West Side - steps away from Central Park, cafes, restaurants and shopping. This apartment has everything you need to make your stay in New York comfortable and enjoyable. 

With the 1, 2 and 3 trains just a half a block away, you can be anywhere in the city within 15-30 min.

Centrally located - only half a block to 1, 2 and 3 trains, M11, M7 bus.

You have to be able to pick up the key by 4pm from Hell's Kitchen.
name: Chic and Cosy studio near Central Park
